metadata.description: Red Panda Pals is a unique collection of artwork celebrating the Red Panda. With 10,000 programmatically generated images of verifiable rarity, this project is a way for the RedPanda Earth Token community to expand their mission of wildlife conservation. Visit [www.redpanda.earth](https://www.redpanda.earth/) to join our Crypto Charity movement and get started. Proceeds from this NFT collection will be sent to charitable organizations across the world!
metadata.name: Red Panda Pal #1
